<H3> <TI>   Army Air Command To Host Latin American Helicopter Fair </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Army Air Command To Host Latin American Helicopter Fair </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY1306190894 Sao Paulo GAZETA MERCANTIL in Portuguese 8 Jun 
94 p 11 </F>

<F P=103> PY1306190894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sao Paulo GAZETA MERCANTIL </F>
<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
