<F P=102>   PA1506131294 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 1730 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1506131294 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>

<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "National Newscast"] </F>
  [Text] To ensure protection for the visiting heads of state 
and delegations, the Colombian military have joined in a single 
strategy and are receiving support from everyone in the country. 
For example, 50 escort motorcycles arrived from Santa Fe de 
Bogota, and a month ago, for greater tranquility, the Colombian 
military met with the heads of security for each of the visiting 
presidents. The last preparations for the security plan 
resulted from these meetings. Even though the plan was for the 
city not to appear to be militarized, it is impossible to 
camouflage the work being done on the ground, in the air, and on 
the water by the 3,000 men who are responsible for ensuring the 
safety of the visiting heads of state. 

</TEXT>

